headline: The Top 5 Analyst Questions From Interpublic Group’s Q2 Earnings Call
summary: Interpublic Group’s second quarter results were received positively by the market, despite a year-on-year revenue decline. Management attributed this to ongoing pressures from major account losses in 2024—particularly in media and healthcare—which weighed on organic growth.
